_sText:
This is my first ever submission to FPSB, so be kind as I'm kinda new to this whole Submission process. This is also my third ever First Person Shooter Map, so if there are any bugs or errors provide them in a constructive manner, not a flaming one.

This is the Spiritual Successor to de_supercede_v2, a previous map I made in which I lost the .bsp file and didn't feel like recreating the same map.

de_apathy_v2 was made entirely by me, Nexolate. You may not copy, edit or redistribute this map anywhere else without my personal permission. Any bugs, suggestions or comments are welcome.

Enjoy.
